Samantha Spiro https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samantha_Spiro 0 Samantha Spiro (born 20 June 1968) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying Barbara Windsor in the stage play Cleo, Camping, Emmanuelle and Dick and the television film Cor, Blimey!, DI Vivien Friend in M.I.T.: Murder Investigation Team, and Melessa Tarly in the HBO series Game of Thrones. She has won two Laurence Olivier Awards. Samantha_Spiro ( born_20_June_1968 ) is an_English_actress .
